Collect requirements
--------------------
pip install pipreqs
pipreqs /path/to/home/project

Command install
---------------
pip install -U spacy
python -m spacy download es

Requirements
------------
spacy==2.0.18
es-core-news-sm==2.0.0
https://github.com/explosion/spacy-models/releases/download/es_core_news_sm-2.0.0/es_core_news_sm-2.0.0.tar.gz#es_core_news_sm

Dockerfile
----------
RUN python -m spacy download es_core_news_sm